{
  "name": "RPlog_A_New_Ally",
  "title": "A New Ally",
  "summary": "On a clear morning along Blake Street in Plaxton City on Caspar, the kind-hearted Corellian Kyyel watches the sunrise and is approached by a haunted, silver-haired woman calling herself Annalise -- in truth the fallen Jedi Jessalyn in disguise, returned to Caspar against her will and burdened by guilt and despair. Sensing her pain, Kyyel gently draws her into conversation, offering food, help, and the promise of secrecy even after she lets her Force-disguise slip enough for him to glimpse her true face. Drawing on his own past as an exile, he speaks with uncanny insight to the very sense of unforgivable failure that torments her, insisting that her grief over her actions proves she is not the foul, twisted creature she believes herself to be. Annalise, terrified of dragging another innocent into her ruin and unable to trust his compassion, refuses his help and flees into the crowds, leaving Kyyel sorrowful but unshaken as he turns toward the beach.",
